race.description: Spelling At Coolmore Mt White Handicap (Bm72)
race.comment: STEEL STRIKE (3) stretches out to the mile for the first time and finally drawn a decent gate. Second-up he pushed forward from a wide draw when a gritty third over 1400m at Warwick Farm. Placed in Listed company last time in and looks close to a win. CHEVAL DE BOIS (15) bounced off his good debut third with a sharp 3.5 len win over 1600m at Scone. Looks to have a ton of upside and worth a throw at the stumps with the 52kg. COVERT THINKING (4) handy mare fitter after two runs back. All three wins have come at the mile and looks over the odds at her good each way price. William Stanley sticks and well in at the weights. EDITING (2) far from disgraced at her first attempt over the mile when sixth to Hyperbolic at this track. Finds a weaker contest with the blinkers going on. Sure to be thereabouts. WILLIE OPPA (10) had no luck two-back at Rosehill, then launched late with a tough victory over this course and distance. Blinkers go on and drops in weight with Grima's 3kg claim. Respect.
